## HOW TO USE THESE PROMPTS

Every prompt here follows the same structure: **Role. Task. Context. Format.**

Claude performs at a different level when it knows who it's being, what it's doing, who you are, and how you want the output delivered. Skipping any of these pieces cuts your results.

Replace every [BRACKETED SECTION] with your specific information before running the prompt. The more specific you are, the better the output.

These are starting points, not scripts. Once Claude responds, keep the conversation going. Push back. Ask for a different angle. Ask it to go deeper. The real value is in the dialogue.

